dc_title_s: A plan of the city's of London, Westminster and borough of Southwark, with the new additional buildings: anno 1720.; New map of London
dc_description_s: "Published with part 68 of Cassell's Old & new London." Includes key to churches and public buildings. "S. Parker delin et sculpt." "E. Weller, litho." 1 map : facsimile, 51 x 66 cm. This map is in the public domain. Please attribute access and use of this digitized map to the Stephen S. Clark Library, University of Michigan Library.
dc_creator_sm: Senex, John, -1740. New map of London, most humbly inscrib'd to the Rt. worshipfull St. Peter Delme t. & Aldermn. of London, 1720. Revised by Ino. Senex.
